{"tid":686002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台料今起落9日雨","createTime":"2018-06-01T01:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T04:10:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"11e69bc9f721184ce346fc593de2a52cb3b261bd","tid":686002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180601/20407937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F20407937&d=2upd%2Bh%2F7CO800nOaBLH%2FZkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c28cdddb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180601%2F20407937&h=c8479f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180601/20407937</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月01日 <br />\n<br />\n天文台料今起落9日雨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180601/large/01la5p20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180601%2Flarge%2F01la5p20.jpg&h=04b1a74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■天文台連續15天錄到達33℃或以上酷熱天氣，昨西環有市民趁氣溫稍降時散步兼賞日落。許頌明攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天文台昨錄得最高氣溫34.8℃，連續15日錄得酷熱天氣，再破紀錄達到「15連熱」。而今年5月平均溫度很大機會達到28.3℃，打破1963年5月28.2℃的紀錄。不過天文台預測酷熱天氣有望紓緩，今起一連九日均下雨。天文台昨又在社交網站宣佈，自1998年設暴雨警告以來，首次在5月未發過暴雨警告，「今年5月紀錄又多一個啦！」<br />\n<br />\n自5月17日起，天文台連續15日錄到達33℃或以上的酷熱天氣。有元朗串燒餐廳昨受不住熱浪，索性停業，貼出公告指「天氣太熱了，夥記（計）受不了，今日休息1天。不便之處，敬請原諒」。天文台預測今日氣溫28至34℃，意味今日亦可能達到酷熱天氣，延續至「16連熱」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n六四晚會當晚料有驟雨<br />\n<br />\n5月截至30日為止，平均溫度為28.236℃，若昨日（31日）平均溫度超過30.2℃，整個5月平均氣溫將達28.3℃，勢打破1963年5月平均氣溫28.2℃的歷史紀錄，成為自1884年以來最炎熱的5月。<br />\n<br />\n天文台指，隨着高空反氣旋在周末期間逐漸減弱，偏東氣流今日稍後抵達廣東沿岸，料今起一連九日下雨，6月4日燭光晚會當日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。<br />\n<br />\n新興農場負責人楊俊武慨嘆，乾旱天氣令農夫叫苦連天。他指，若未來數日持續天陰有雨，尚可挽救部份農作物，最怕驟雨後持續幾小時猛烈陽光，農作物會受不住死亡。今年5月天文台錄得總雨量僅57.5毫米，料列歷來第九少雨5月。根據記錄，最少雨量的5月是1963年，當時整月僅得6毫米雨量。<br />\n<br />\n■記者潘柏林  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n15連熱　無自來水東平洲熱到井枯<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n廟街地標「單眼佬涼茶」暫別街坊"},{"pid":"1d92f4db2bfcb84362f598687e4bb67e3c187b89","tid":686002,"uid":15394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T01:48:20.000Z","msg":"天文台既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405f0cf24f01f0042d027f14bb018ff4e0f30250","tid":686002,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d92f4db2bfcb84362f598687e4bb67e3c187b89","tid":686002,"uid":15394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T01:48:20.000Z","msg":"天文台既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"聽下好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7925d77030cf044834259dae53d84054915ee05e","tid":686002,"uid":34551,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六四晚會當晚料有驟雨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81d4550e8ff698fe5fd0e95e6bbca789132463d","tid":686002,"uid":121040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"六四邪壇 皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"447746ac3868b09400efc50c760ec7fe975eb459","tid":686002,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018